<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Reset Your MyTrackr Password</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f5; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .header { background-color: #101828; color: #ffffff; padding: 20px 40px; text-align: center; }
        .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0; }
        .content { padding: 40px; color: #344054; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #0b4a6f; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 24px 0; transition: background-color 0.2s; }
        .btn:hover { background-color: #083a57; text-decoration: none !important; color: white !important;}
        .footer { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 20px 40px; text-align: center; color: #667085; font-size: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #eaecf0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2 class="logo">MyTrackr</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1 style="color: #101828; margin-top: 0;">Password Reset Request</h1>
            <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset your MyTrackr password. Click the button below to choose a new one. This link will expire in 15 minutes.</p>
            <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="btn">Reset My Password</a>
            <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #667085; margin-top: 30px;">
                If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:<br>
                <a href="{{resetLink}}" style="color: #0b4a6f; word-break: break-all;">{{resetLink}}</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 MyTrackr. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
